WEBVTT

00:01.633 --> 00:04.436
The violence in Chicago has
now touched elected officials.

00:04.469 --> 00:07.105
Outspoken Alderman James Burton
of the 24th ward

00:07.139 --> 00:08.641
was gunned down this morning

00:08.673 --> 00:10.709
- in the financial district.
- Streets and Sanitation worker

00:10.743 --> 00:12.310
found him an hour ago.

00:12.343 --> 00:15.814
GSW to the head,
T.O.D. between 2:00 a.m.,

00:15.848 --> 00:17.382
3:00 a.m. based on lividity.

00:17.416 --> 00:19.352
- Witnesses?
- No one's come forward.

00:19.385 --> 00:21.621
Yeah, this place is
really dead after hours, Sarge.

00:21.653 --> 00:23.388
I doubt anybody was here.

00:23.422 --> 00:25.257
Pockets turned inside and out.

00:25.291 --> 00:27.292
Wallet, watch, and cell phone are gone.

00:27.326 --> 00:28.628
Any signs of a struggle?

00:28.661 --> 00:31.264
Nope, looks like a robbery gone wrong.

00:31.297 --> 00:33.666
Know what Alderman Burton
was doing down here?

00:33.698 --> 00:35.400
Drinking at the Crown Pub.

00:35.433 --> 00:37.335
Bartender said he was with a banker,

00:37.368 --> 00:39.204
Rudy Finnegan, till closing.

00:39.237 --> 00:40.839
We'll go talk to him.

00:40.872 --> 00:42.474
I heard this alderman said

00:42.508 --> 00:44.644
cops only care about white victims.

00:44.676 --> 00:46.179
I'd love to tell this jackass

00:46.212 --> 00:47.413
I'm working double overtime

00:47.445 --> 00:49.481
to help find the guy who killed him.

00:50.149 --> 00:51.384
Hank.

00:51.417 --> 00:53.753
Hey, that's great news
about your daughter.

00:53.786 --> 00:55.288
I hear she's going to be okay.

00:55.320 --> 00:58.690
Yeah, doctors did a great job.

00:58.723 --> 01:00.292
- Burton, huh?
- Yeah.

01:00.326 --> 01:02.561
You know he and the mayor
were very close friends.

01:02.594 --> 01:05.197
Yeah, the mayor would like
your team to work this quick.

01:05.230 --> 01:06.565
Understood.

01:06.599 --> 01:08.600
Detective Olinsky.

01:10.635 --> 01:12.539
We'd like a word.

01:15.808 --> 01:18.277
What's this about?

01:18.310 --> 01:20.680
Not here. Down at headquarters.

01:21.579 --> 01:22.527
It's important, Al.

01:22.559 --> 01:25.005
- We wouldn't be here if it wasn't.
- Get off me, man.

