01:34.760 --> 01:37.097
What the hell is this about?

01:52.510 --> 01:54.212
Thanks for coming in, Detective Olinsky.

01:54.245 --> 01:55.447
So why am I here?

01:55.480 --> 01:57.382
We need to ask you some questions.

01:57.415 --> 01:59.685
- About?
- Kevin Bingham.

02:01.287 --> 02:04.257
He murdered Hank Voight's son.

02:04.290 --> 02:06.459
They dug his body up about six weeks ago

02:06.492 --> 02:08.759
at a Super Mart construction site.

02:08.794 --> 02:10.530
So?

02:10.562 --> 02:12.298
You meet the guy?

02:13.932 --> 02:15.367
Okay, look.

02:15.401 --> 02:19.605
Third party DNA was found
on Bingham's body.

02:19.638 --> 02:20.740
Yours.

02:22.241 --> 02:23.476
Al.

02:23.508 --> 02:25.377
Can you explain how your hair

02:25.411 --> 02:27.413
ended up on the victim?

02:29.548 --> 02:31.769
Lawyer.

